    <p>
      This knowledge base covers the core concepts, research directions, and real-world applications of <strong>Embodied Intelligence</strong> — the field of building AI systems that learn through physical interaction with the world.
    </p>

    <div class="callout callout-blue">
      <div class="callout-title">💡 What is Embodied AI?</div>
      <p style="margin:0">Unlike cloud-based AI that processes text and images on servers, embodied agents have physical bodies. They perceive through cameras and touch, reason about spatial relationships, and act in the real world — where gravity, friction, and uncertainty cannot be ignored.</p>
    </div>

